00033 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00034 /* USB Device descriptor setting                                                                            */
00035 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00036 // <h> USB Device descriptor setting
00037 //   <o0> USB Specification Release number (bcdUSB)
00038 //      <0x0200=> USB 2.0
00039 //      <0x0110=> USB 1.1
00040 //      <0x0100=> USB 1.0
00041 //   <o1> USB Class code (assigned by the USB-IF)
00042 //      <0x00=> Use class information in the Interface Descriptors (0x00)
00043 //      <0x02=> Communications and CDC Control (CDC, 0x02)
00044 //      <0xDC=> Diagnostic Device (0xDC)
00045 //      <0xEF=> Miscellaneous (0xEF)
00046 //      <0xFF=> Vendor Specific (0xFF)
00047 //   <o2> USB Subclass code (assigned by the USB-IF) <0x0-0xFF:1>
00048 //   <o3> USB Protocol code (assigned by the USB-IF) <0x0-0xFF:1>
00049 //   <o4> USB Vendor ID <0x0-0xFFFF:1>
00050 //   <o5> USB Product ID <0x0-0xFFFF:1>
00051 //   <o6> USB Device Version <0x0-0xFFFF:1>
00052 //   <o7.0> USB String descriptor - Manufacturer
00053 //   <o8.0> USB String descriptor - Product
00054 //   <o9.0> USB String descriptor - Device serial number
00055 //   <o10> USB Number of possible configurations <0-255:1>
00056 #define DESC_BCDUSB               (0x0110)
00057 #define DESC_BDEVCLASS            (0x00)
00058 #define DESC_BDEVSUBCLASS         (0x00)
00059 #define DESC_BDEVPROTOCOL         (0x00)
00060 #define DESC_IDVENDOR             (0x04D9)
00061 #define DESC_IDPRODUCT            (0x8008)
00062 #define DESC_BCDDEVICE            (0x0100)
00063 #define DESC_IMANUFACTURE         (1)
00064 #define DESC_IPRODUCT             (1)
00065 #define DESC_ISERIALNUM           (1)
00066 #define DESC_INUMCONFN            (1)
00067 // </h>
00068 
00069 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00070 /* USB Device Descriptor definition. DO NOT MODIFY.                                                         */
00071 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00072 #if (DESC_BDEVCLASS == 0x0 & DESC_BDEVSUBCLASS != 0x0)
00073 #error "DESC_BDEVSUBCLASS must be reset to zero when the DESC_BDEVCLASS is equal to zero."
00074 #endif
00075 #define DESC_WMAXPACKETSIZE0      (_EP0LEN)
00076 #define DESC_STR_MAN              (1 * DESC_IMANUFACTURE)
00077 #define DESC_STR_PRD              (2 * DESC_IPRODUCT)
00078 #define DESC_STR_SER              (3 * DESC_ISERIALNUM)
00079 #define DESC_NUM_STRING           (1 + 3)

00081 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00082 /* USB Device descriptor                                                                                    */
00083 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00084 __ALIGN4 static uc8 guUSB_DeviceDesc[] =
00085 {
00086   /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00087   /* Device descriptor                                                                                      */
00088   /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00089                               /* Field            Size Description                                          */
00090                               /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00091   DESC_LEN_DEV,               // bLength             1 Size of this descriptor in bytes
00092   DESC_TYPE_01_DEV,           // bDescriptorType     1 DEVICE Descriptor Type
00093   DESC_H2B(DESC_BCDUSB),      // bcdUSB              2 USB Specification Release Number
00094   DESC_BDEVCLASS,             // bDeviceClass        1 Class code (assigned by the USB-IF)
00095   DESC_BDEVSUBCLASS,          // bDeviceSubClass     1 Subclass code (assigned by the USB-IF)
00096   DESC_BDEVPROTOCOL,          // bDeviceProtocol     1 Protocol code (assigned by the USB-IF)
00097   DESC_WMAXPACKETSIZE0,       // wMaxPacketSize0     1 Maximum packet size for endpoint zero
00098   DESC_H2B(DESC_IDVENDOR),    // idVendor            2 Vendor ID (assigned by USB-IF)
00099   DESC_H2B(DESC_IDPRODUCT),   // idProduct           2 Product ID (assigned by manufacturer)
00100   DESC_H2B(DESC_BCDDEVICE),   // bcdDevice           2 Device release number
00101   DESC_STR_MAN,               // iManufacturer       1 Index of string descriptor (Manufacturer)
00102   DESC_STR_PRD,               // iProduct            1 Index of string descriptor (Product)
00103   DESC_STR_SER,               // iSerialNumber       1 Index of string descriptor (Serial Number)
00104   DESC_INUMCONFN,             // iNumConfigurations  1 Number of possible configuration
00105 };

00108 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00109 /* USB Configuration descriptor setting                                                                     */
00110 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00111 // <h> USB Configuration descriptor setting
00112 //   <o0.0> Self-powered
00113 //     <i> Bit 6 of bmAttributes
00114 //   <o1.0> Remote Wakeup
00115 //     <i> Bit 5 of bmAttributes
00116 //   <o2> USB Device maximum power (mA) < 2-512:2>
00117 #define DESC_BMATTR_SELF_POWER        (0)
00118 #define DESC_BMATTR_REMOTE_WAKEUP     (0)
00119 #define DESC_BMAXPOWER                (100)
00120 // </h>
00121 
00122 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00123 /* USB Configuration Descriptor definition. DO NOT MODIFY.                                                  */
00124 /*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00125 #define DESC_BMATTRIBUTES        (0x80 | (DESC_BMATTR_SELF_POWER << 6) | (DESC_BMATTR_REMOTE_WAKEUP << 5))
00126 #define DESC_TOTAL_LEN           DESC_H2B((DESC_LEN_CONFN_T + RETARGET_DLEN))
00127

00139   DESC_TYPE_02_CONFN,         // bDescriptorType     1 CONFIGURATION Descriptor Type

00141   RETARGET_INF,               // bNumberInterface    1 Number of interfaces supported by this configuration

00144   DESC_BMATTRIBUTES,          // bmAttributes        1 Configuration characteristics
